title: Herb Alpert and the Tijuana Brass - Going Places [RTR-Rip] [CDM]

Technical Info:
Sourced from original release on 1/4" Reel-to-Reel Tape, 4-track, 7.5IPS.
Playback source: Akai Custom Deck X150-D

Output Format: Single-file WAV, 16-bit PCM @ 44.1kHz, WAV/CUE.

This is an uncompressed, gapless CD master that is ready to be burned to disk. Though it is only a single WAV file, the resulting CD will have 12 tracks.

[A multi-file FLAC release for computer/audio device playback will soon follow.]
